window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A SPIRITUAL DISPLAY!</b></p> <p>In this hotly-requested collection of after-stories, the colorful residents of the Spirit Realm take center stage! Get a glimpse into the lives of Kinme, Ginme, Toochika and more, deftly weaved together with hints of Kaori and Suimei's happily ever after! Plus, a selection of three short stories expanded exclusively for the finale!</p>"; 
